23:28.011 --> 23:30.680
Because I didn't want to
scare Quinn, all right?

23:30.764 --> 23:32.315
I don't remember
how I got there.

23:32.399 --> 23:33.799
I can't remember
how I got home!

23:33.850 --> 23:35.818
I can't remember anything.

23:37.487 --> 23:41.407
♪ And I promised you...

23:41.491 --> 23:43.892
Well, fix it
before someone gets hurt.

24:00.020 --> 24:02.620
Why didn't you tell me
the truth?

24:02.687 --> 24:05.839
Because I don't know
what's happening,

24:05.924 --> 24:07.958
and I didn't want
to scare you.

24:08.009 --> 24:09.727
The only thing
that scares me

24:09.794 --> 24:11.812
