Ass matters.

26:00.922 --> 26:02.089
Does "not Alex"
have a good ass?

26:02.173 --> 26:04.407
♪ Baby, why don't you
lie down? ♪

26:04.459 --> 26:07.127
Does she?

26:07.212 --> 26:09.780
Um...
I-I don't know.

26:12.634 --> 26:16.737
I got to...
I'll be in the stockroom.

26:16.855 --> 26:20.224
♪ When I hold you,
everything slows down ♪

26:20.275 --> 26:25.095
♪ when I know you
inside and out ♪

26:25.146 --> 26:31.869
♪ I wanna show you
there's no such thing as time ♪

26:34.789 --> 26:36.573
Hey.

26:38.993 --> 26:40.711
How you doing?

26:40.778 --> 26:43.530
♪ So take a deep breath
tonight ♪

26:43.598 --> 26:45.382
