trust myself with them again.

27:00.582 --> 27:03.633
♪ And when I hold you...

27:03.685 --> 27:08.238
I'm not sure how I could have
let something like this happen.

27:08.306 --> 27:10.774
♪ When I know you
inside and out ♪

27:10.825 --> 27:14.111
♪ I wanna show you...

27:14.162 --> 27:18.982
When, uh, when Jamie was 5,
I think...

27:19.033 --> 27:23.653
Nathan and I were in the kitchen
at night, arguing.

27:23.705 --> 27:26.540
And I remember
looking out the window,

27:26.624 --> 27:30.010
and I saw him playing basketball
by the pool.

27:30.094 --> 27:33.847
Somewhere,
between all the yelling

27:33.932 --> 27:36.350
and the next time
I looked out,

27:36.434 --> 27:38.335
he had disappeared

27:38.386 --> 27:42.189
and, uh, I went outside...

27:42.273 --> 27:46.777
