facedown in the pool.

27:46.844 --> 27:49.229
♪ When I hold you,
everything slows down ♪

27:49.314 --> 27:52.482
And we didn't know how long
he'd been out there.

27:52.534 --> 27:54.684
And, um...

27:54.736 --> 27:57.704
Nathan pulled him in.

27:57.789 --> 28:00.374
