for that.

28:23.531 --> 28:27.935
But I did eventually,

28:28.019 --> 28:31.438
and you will, too,

28:31.522 --> 28:36.360
because your babies
aren't going anywhere.

28:36.411 --> 28:38.145
Your job doesn't end.

28:38.212 --> 28:41.832
And the best that we,
as parents, can do

28:41.899 --> 28:46.870
is just love them with all
of our hearts and...

28:46.921 --> 28:49.339
Try and do better
next time.

29:09.727 --> 29:11.979
I hear the scallops
are great here.

29:17.035 --> 29:19.453
