Thanks.

29:44.295 --> 29:46.897
I'll have the same.

29:55.806 --> 29:58.525
It's good to see you,
Clay.

29:58.609 --> 30:00.327
It's been a while.

30:00.411 --> 30:02.245
How have you been?

30:02.313 --> 30:05.032
