things could be better.

30:07.151 --> 30:09.670
What about Sara?

30:09.737 --> 30:13.707
Do you still see her,
have conversations with her?

30:13.791 --> 30:15.825
No.

30:15.877 --> 30:17.344
Have you met
someone else?

30:17.428 --> 30:19.496
Her name's Quinn.

30:19.547 --> 30:21.014
She's real.

30:21.099 --> 30:23.433
