to see Nathan tonight?

31:27.165 --> 31:29.783
Ohh, I can't wait.

31:29.867 --> 31:32.452
You know,
Julian stopped by today.

31:34.705 --> 31:37.841
Brooke,
you have to forgive him.

31:37.908 --> 31:41.128
How am I gonna trust him
with them again?

31:41.212 --> 31:43.213
